1️⃣ Create a new task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
{
  "title": "Design Homepage",
  "description": "Create UI for the landing page",
  "assignedTo": "Muskaan",
  "status": "PENDING"   // Can be PENDING, IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETED
}


2️⃣ Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks





3️⃣ Get Task by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1




4️⃣ Get Tasks by Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/status/PENDING



5️⃣ Update a Task
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
{
  "title": "Design Homepage Updated",
  "description": "Update UI with new colors",
  "assignedTo": "Muskaan",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}



6 Update Task Status Only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1/status




7️⃣ Delete a Task
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
